{"version":1,"content":"<html>\n<body>\n\n<p>發佈時間：13:00 2026-04-23 HKT</p>\n<img alt=\"Dr.Martens開倉直擊低至3折！招牌短靴/牛津鞋/瑪莉珍/學生鞋$250起入手 學生額外9折！\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f61e83e9e4ff3bd725a90fac7c04f2d6/2026-04/20260423_LIFE_DRMARTENS.png\"/>\n<p>Dr. Martens開倉｜Dr. Martens一直是街頭潮流與實用耐穿的經典代表，深受學生及時尚愛好者追捧，其中瑪莉珍、學生鞋等更成為多款Threads話題產品。近日與OnTheList聯手相隔9年再度推出限時開倉活動，精選鞋履低至3折起售，部分款式更低至$250，學生更可享額外9折優惠，性價比極高。</p>\n<h2>Dr.Martens開倉3折起！招牌短靴/牛津鞋/瑪莉珍/學生鞋$250起入手</h2>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/4097bd826fa6a64eea4587eac4310390/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_41.jpeg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/088eef786f1793d2655cb438805b4e4d/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_42_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d4df85df337b541706ec3fccd0cbb4e9/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_42.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$490\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/46a72a84de27a1c9bb8aa9f140cf69ff/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_43_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$490\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/745ca29e433de559a3de1a302477d391/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_43.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$590\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b83c8a9ded930d3e1bcddde631c9cd5e/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_44_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$590\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af37ac426e832deb4fa70c68300b24ee/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_44.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$590\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cfd2e0fb0d03a8056c37b31a4d8f05b/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_45_1_.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$590\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/5dfcad5d6be39c18cd56f57d68f47ebe/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_11_18_45.jpeg\"/>\n<img alt=\"$590\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d57e9b0aee98af093cb5efde85781c16/2026-04/WhatsApp_Image_2026-04-23_at_